  /dx x0 x1 sub 3 div def 
  /dy y0 y1 sub 3 div def 
  x0 dx sub y0 dy add x1 y1 ArrowA
  x0 dx add y0 dy add x0 2 mul x1 sub y1 ArrowB 
  curveto 
